BigJob

This directory contains different implementations of BigJob.

The BigJob package including example code is located in the generic directory:

- generic/ SAGA-BigJob supporting different backends (Globus, PBSPro, fork via SAGA) and different coordination & communication frameworks (Advert, Redis, ZMQ)


Experimental
- cloud/ - BJ supporting EC2/Eucalyptus backends (based on cmd-utils)
- azure/ - BJ supporting Windows Azure
- condor/ - BJ supporting Condor
